      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUINATION (3) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only a neck from the winner FUMBLES in second(17.75) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from eight starts. Rates highly and will give a great sight. BLACK KERMARO (7) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his blistering 17.53 win at this track over 324m. Should be in this for a long way. HELLO AERIAL (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (29.87) at Gosford. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Expecting another good run. WOOLGOOLGA (2) cannot be dismissed although new to this distance.",
